Shizuka Minamoto <p id="Pink6">(源 静香, Minamoto Shizuka) </p> ,<p id="Pink4"> nicknamed Shizuka-chan (しずかちゃん) is a smart, kind and pretty girl.</p> She is often represented by the colour pink, and is seen wearing a pink shirt and skirt. The word 'Shizuka (しずか)' means 'Quiet'. She is Nobita's best friend and love-interest. She does not shun Nobita due to his failing grades, lazy disposition or constant failures. In fact, she often tries to encourage him to do better, though she usually fails to convince him.
